%%{init: {'theme': 'dark'}}%%
flowchart LR
    Candidate[Memory Candidate<br/>from Chat or Deep Agent] --> Extract[Memory Extractor]
    Extract --> Classify[Memory Classifier<br/>type + sensitivity]
    Classify --> Govern[Memory Governance Service]
    
    Govern --> PHI{PHI / Clinical<br/>Content Detected?}
    PHI -->|Yes| Block[Block + Audit]
    PHI -->|No| RoleCheck{Role + Consent<br/>Allowed?}
    
    RoleCheck -->|No| Block
    RoleCheck -->|Yes| Minimize[PHI Minimization + Minimized Text]
    Minimize --> Store[(Hindsight Memory<br/>memory_records)]
    
    Store --> Audit[Write Memory Policy Decision + Audit Event]
    
    classDef block fill:#7f1d1d,stroke:#ef4444,color:#fff
    class Block block
